Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:13.05,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HC43F20&\bord2\blur3\pos(875,610)}加油超然仔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:41.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-H-GBK\fs90\pos(430,540)}想要重建家园
